These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, milk
1. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |
| Beverage   | milk | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-2::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, firefighter
1. the teacher is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
2. the firefighter is on the right of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |      2      |
| Job   | teacher | firefighter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | board-games | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, d&b
1. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of disco##1
2. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | disco |

